" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/2/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2">Bestemmelsene i paragrafen her forutsetter aksept fra ESA, jf. Rdir. 1998/18/EF, fastsatt 17. mars 1998, artikkel 7.</article></section><section class="section" data-name="kapII" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/" id="kapittel-2" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2000-08-31-889/KAPITTEL_2" data-partID="k2"><h2 data-text-align="center">II</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-2-ledd-1">Endringene trer i kraft 1. oktober 2000.</article></section></main></body></html>